1
00:00:13,540 --> 00:00:15,780
♪Trap my frame♪

2
00:00:15,980 --> 00:00:20,060
♪Plagues demand I bow in shame♪

3
00:00:20,780 --> 00:00:22,940
♪Snare my soul♪

4
00:00:23,020 --> 00:00:27,100
♪Rules command I swallow my pride♪

5
00:00:27,260 --> 00:00:30,620
♪Mock my way♪

6
00:00:30,900 --> 00:00:34,060
♪Chained me where I must stay♪

7
00:00:34,420 --> 00:00:36,780
♪Taught me to kneel, not to speak♪

8
00:00:37,020 --> 00:00:41,220
♪And to let my life pass by in silence♪

9
00:00:42,100 --> 00:00:44,100
♪But I heard the wind♪

10
00:00:44,220 --> 00:00:45,900
♪From the sea and the sky♪

11
00:00:46,180 --> 00:00:47,660
♪It said don't bend♪

12
00:00:47,780 --> 00:00:49,820
♪Bow your head, and your chains begin♪

13
00:00:49,940 --> 00:00:51,380
♪You are the wave♪

14
00:00:51,500 --> 00:00:53,300
♪And the wind that won't behave♪

15
00:00:53,380 --> 00:00:56,340
♪How could you be chained?♪

16
00:00:56,740 --> 00:00:58,740
♪Untamed, uncaged, unclaimed♪

17
00:00:58,780 --> 00:01:00,540
♪You're the blade in my gaze♪

18
00:01:00,620 --> 00:01:02,420
♪This world will leave you no space♪

19
00:01:02,500 --> 00:01:04,220
♪Then pierce it with your blaze♪

20
00:01:04,220 --> 00:01:06,100
♪My silent grind♪

21
00:01:06,100 --> 00:01:08,060
♪My aching pain♪

22
00:01:08,060 --> 00:01:10,300
♪Will one day turn...♪

23
00:01:11,860 --> 00:01:14,620
♪I am who I am♪

24
00:01:14,620 --> 00:01:18,140
♪My greatest ambition♪

25
00:01:18,220 --> 00:01:21,300
♪If the world can't contain me♪

26
00:01:21,380 --> 00:01:24,940
♪Then I'll break through it♪

27
00:01:25,420 --> 00:01:26,940
♪Become who I am♪

28
00:01:26,940 --> 00:01:28,260
[Wild Ambition Bloom]

29
00:01:28,260 --> 00:01:29,980
[Adapted from Stone and Water's novel,
The Uncaged Flame]

30
00:01:29,980 --> 00:01:32,980
[Episode 33]

31
00:01:33,280 --> 00:01:35,260
This leaves us with only two choices.

32
00:01:35,920 --> 00:01:38,020
Surrender to him now

33
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:39,380
or

34
00:01:39,870 --> 00:01:41,380
surrender to him before bankruptcy.

35
00:01:44,710 --> 00:01:45,570
Will you?

36
00:01:50,710 --> 00:01:51,330
Here's my idea.

37
00:01:56,920 --> 00:01:57,900
If it comes up heads,

38
00:01:58,070 --> 00:01:58,930
you'll hunt for supplies;

39
00:01:58,950 --> 00:02:00,210
I'll convince customers

40
00:02:00,230 --> 00:02:01,380
of delivery postponement.

41
00:02:01,710 --> 00:02:02,660
If heads down,

42
00:02:02,680 --> 00:02:03,460
I'll hunt for supplies;

43
00:02:03,480 --> 00:02:04,460
you'll convince the customers.

44
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:05,820
Go ahead.

45
00:02:20,560 --> 00:02:22,220
Given the changed situation,

46
00:02:22,310 --> 00:02:24,820
could we delay delivering the goods?

47
00:02:25,280 --> 00:02:26,060
Absolutely not.

48
00:02:26,280 --> 00:02:28,010
We've booked wagons

49
00:02:28,030 --> 00:02:29,540
waiting for delivery.

50
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:30,730
No delays allowed.

51
00:02:32,030 --> 00:02:32,820
Ms. Chu,

52
00:02:33,240 --> 00:02:35,220
we've run out of the raw herbs you want.

53
00:02:35,310 --> 00:02:37,100
Let alone a whole bag,

54
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:39,660
I couldn't even produce a single stick.

55
00:02:40,120 --> 00:02:42,500
If you don't believe, look around.

56
00:02:48,080 --> 00:02:49,820
Mr. Yu, by how things stand now,

57
00:02:49,840 --> 00:02:51,450
it's hard to fulfill this order.

58
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:54,500
Then compensate.

59
00:02:54,520 --> 00:02:55,340
Sure, we will.

60
00:02:55,360 --> 00:02:57,100
But could we reduce the amount?

61
00:02:58,430 --> 00:02:59,220
No.

62
00:02:59,590 --> 00:03:01,060
Compensate based on those figures

63
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:02,290
in the contract.

64
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:06,780
It'll drive us

65
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:08,850
straight into bankruptcy!

66
00:03:09,870 --> 00:03:11,500
None of my business.

67
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:14,130
I can't help.

68
00:03:15,240 --> 00:03:16,340
We could offer higher prices.

69
00:03:16,360 --> 00:03:18,820
Let me be frank.

70
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:20,060
Even if you increase the offer,

71
00:03:20,310 --> 00:03:21,340
I simply cannot sell to you.

72
00:03:22,310 --> 00:03:23,100
Why?

73
00:03:23,750 --> 00:03:25,220
Mr. Xia...

74
00:03:28,910 --> 00:03:29,610
I see.

75
00:03:44,280 --> 00:03:46,340
I've checked with every herbal supplier

76
00:03:46,710 --> 00:03:48,500
in Shanghai and the surrounding areas.

77
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:50,130
Some have no stock left.

78
00:03:50,430 --> 00:03:51,730
As to those with inventory,

79
00:03:51,750 --> 00:03:53,010
some are controlled by Xia Yuan,

80
00:03:53,590 --> 00:03:55,660
and some store their goods too far away

81
00:03:56,080 --> 00:03:57,450
to deliver before the Chinese New Year.

82
00:04:00,560 --> 00:04:02,660
Our customers have the same demands.

83
00:04:03,030 --> 00:04:04,410
Either deliver on time

84
00:04:04,430 --> 00:04:05,260
or compensate.

85
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:09,290
Seems we must pay the penalties.

86
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:12,610
But we don't have funds.

87
00:04:14,630 --> 00:04:16,250
My house and your car

88
00:04:16,750 --> 00:04:17,610
are worth something.

89
00:04:19,190 --> 00:04:20,460
A drop in the bucket.

90
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:22,700
So

91
00:04:22,870 --> 00:04:24,220
are we going to sell

92
00:04:24,240 --> 00:04:25,020
our brand?

93
00:04:26,950 --> 00:04:28,370
What does he want?

94
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:31,220
Wen's Pharmacy.

95
00:04:33,870 --> 00:04:34,540
Yes.

96
00:04:39,040 --> 00:04:39,850
Today?

97
00:04:41,680 --> 00:04:42,340
Alright.

98
00:04:43,310 --> 00:04:43,850
Got it!

99
00:04:49,190 --> 00:04:50,140
Guess who?

100
00:04:57,630 --> 00:04:58,780
I heard

101
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:02,290
you're going bankrupt.

102
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:05,930
Just rumors.

103
00:05:06,720 --> 00:05:07,460
Not true.

104
00:05:09,830 --> 00:05:10,730
I've also heard

105
00:05:11,720 --> 00:05:14,370
Xia Yuan cut off your raw herbs supply,

106
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:17,490
so you can't fulfill existing orders

107
00:05:17,510 --> 00:05:19,900
and have to compensate your customers.

108
00:05:22,480 --> 00:05:23,250
Mr. Tian,

109
00:05:24,830 --> 00:05:27,490
he is also our shareholder!

110
00:05:28,040 --> 00:05:30,700
Would he do that to harm

111
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:31,660
everyone involved?

112
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:38,610
Stubborn!

113
00:05:41,190 --> 00:05:43,290
Did you call us here today

114
00:05:43,920 --> 00:05:44,980
for anything else?

115
00:05:45,240 --> 00:05:46,580
Let me be blunt.

116
00:05:47,680 --> 00:05:50,730
For the rare herbs
you're desperately seeking,

117
00:05:50,950 --> 00:05:53,250
I happen to have plenty right now.

118
00:05:55,950 --> 00:05:57,850
Stop boasting!

119
00:05:57,870 --> 00:05:58,660
Don't believe me?

120
00:05:59,680 --> 00:06:01,100
No supplier in Jiangsu and Zhejiang

121
00:06:01,120 --> 00:06:02,410
had stock left.

122
00:06:02,430 --> 00:06:04,340
What if I do have some?

123
00:06:04,480 --> 00:06:05,100
Let it be.

124
00:06:05,200 --> 00:06:06,140
None of our business.

125
00:06:06,260 --> 00:06:07,460
Are you selling it to us?

126
00:06:08,780 --> 00:06:10,220
Who knows?

127
00:06:10,750 --> 00:06:11,820
Even if you are,

128
00:06:11,840 --> 00:06:13,050
we won't buy from you.

129
00:06:13,160 --> 00:06:13,970
Why?

130
00:06:14,190 --> 00:06:14,780
Shaohua.

131
00:06:15,750 --> 00:06:17,170
Don't be fooled.

132
00:06:17,190 --> 00:06:19,170
He has no stock, just fooling us!

133
00:06:20,310 --> 00:06:21,370
Even if we assume

134
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:22,930
he does have stock,

135
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:24,530
would he sell that to us?

136
00:06:24,750 --> 00:06:26,900
He wants us to be crushed by Xia Yuan.

137
00:06:27,190 --> 00:06:28,260
I'm selling it!

138
00:06:28,800 --> 00:06:29,700
But I won't buy!

139
00:06:29,920 --> 00:06:30,460
Shut your mouth!

140
00:06:31,990 --> 00:06:32,660
Mr. Tian,

141
00:06:33,120 --> 00:06:35,100
do you intend to sell those herbs

142
00:06:35,120 --> 00:06:36,050
to us?

143
00:06:36,220 --> 00:06:36,820
Exactly!

144
00:06:37,310 --> 00:06:39,220
But at five times the market rate.

145
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:40,850
What? Five times?

146
00:06:40,870 --> 00:06:42,370
Why don't you just rob a bank?

147
00:06:42,870 --> 00:06:45,140
If I do, cops will arrest me.

148
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:47,100
But if I rob you,
they won't lift a finger!

149
00:06:47,190 --> 00:06:48,100
Besides,

150
00:06:48,120 --> 00:06:50,170
to rob a bank will bring me only cash.

151
00:06:50,190 --> 00:06:52,460
But to rob you will bring me cash

152
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:54,100
and annoy Xia Yuan!

153
00:06:54,430 --> 00:06:55,700
Happy to just think about it.

154
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:56,900
Wen Zhiqiu,

155
00:06:57,510 --> 00:06:59,050
let alone the fivefold price,

156
00:06:59,480 --> 00:07:00,730
even if he offers them for free,

157
00:07:00,750 --> 00:07:01,660
we must not accept.

158
00:07:01,840 --> 00:07:02,490
But

159
00:07:02,990 --> 00:07:04,970
if we can't secure the raw herbs now,

160
00:07:04,990 --> 00:07:06,020
we'll go broke.

161
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:07,340
I'd rather go broke.

162
00:07:07,430 --> 00:07:09,020
Then Xia Yuan will get what he wants.

163
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:10,260
Precisely!

164
00:07:10,750 --> 00:07:11,930
After all,

165
00:07:12,190 --> 00:07:13,970
traitor Xia Yuan

166
00:07:14,190 --> 00:07:15,610
is far more hateful than me.

167
00:07:15,630 --> 00:07:17,410
You're despicable, no better!

168
00:07:17,430 --> 00:07:19,460
You schemer!

169
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:20,490
Two of a kind!

170
00:07:20,510 --> 00:07:22,050
Today, I won't let you succeed.

171
00:07:22,070 --> 00:07:23,340
Today, I'll succeed!

172
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:23,850
Stop!

173
00:07:24,190 --> 00:07:24,970
Enough talking to her.

174
00:07:25,070 --> 00:07:26,700
Tell me yes or no.

175
00:07:26,720 --> 00:07:27,220
Yes!

176
00:07:27,840 --> 00:07:29,490
But we simply can't

177
00:07:29,510 --> 00:07:31,020
afford the high price.

178
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:32,020
Wen Zhiqiu,

179
00:07:32,240 --> 00:07:34,140
he almost ruined me and Bai Bingxin!

180
00:07:34,160 --> 00:07:35,610
We wish we could eat his flesh
and sleep on his skin.

181
00:07:35,630 --> 00:07:36,930
Yet you're buying his goods.

182
00:07:37,240 --> 00:07:38,260
Isn't that pure humiliation?

183
00:07:38,280 --> 00:07:39,610
I aim to humiliate you!

184
00:07:39,630 --> 00:07:40,900
Let's say four times?

185
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:42,370
We still can't pay!

186
00:07:42,390 --> 00:07:43,610
We will never bow to you!

187
00:07:43,630 --> 00:07:45,100
But I will make you bow!

188
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:46,410
Three times, okay?

189
00:07:46,430 --> 00:07:47,170
Mr. Tian,

190
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:49,580
we don't have enough funds now.

191
00:07:49,680 --> 00:07:51,610
What price will work for you?

192
00:07:51,870 --> 00:07:53,660
The market rate and I'll take it!

193
00:07:53,840 --> 00:07:54,610
Let's go.

194
00:07:55,070 --> 00:07:56,970
I'm sick of taking a second look at him.

195
00:07:56,990 --> 00:07:58,460
Alright, the market rate!

196
00:07:58,550 --> 00:08:00,410
We must not let him win!

197
00:08:00,430 --> 00:08:02,410
I'm determined to win!

198
00:08:04,160 --> 00:08:04,970
Sign the contract now!

199
00:08:05,870 --> 00:08:06,900
Why don't you leave first?

200
00:08:08,120 --> 00:08:09,020
What do you mean?

201
00:08:09,070 --> 00:08:10,900
Just let him humiliate us?

202
00:08:12,870 --> 00:08:15,260
Chu Shaohua, I'm the boss!

203
00:08:15,430 --> 00:08:17,370
When it comes to business,
my word is law!

204
00:08:22,630 --> 00:08:23,700
I look down on you.

205
00:08:31,990 --> 00:08:34,490
Women and petty men
are hardest to deal with.

206
00:08:35,990 --> 00:08:37,250
Please excuse me, Mr. Tian.

207
00:08:38,510 --> 00:08:39,180
No harm done.

208
00:08:39,750 --> 00:08:42,010
Seeing your infighting brings me joy.

209
00:08:45,720 --> 00:08:46,700
Back then,

210
00:08:47,030 --> 00:08:48,130
I thought

211
00:08:48,630 --> 00:08:50,820
you and Xia Yuan were staging

212
00:08:50,840 --> 00:08:52,420
a show just for me.

213
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:55,060
But as he crushed you brutally,

214
00:08:55,080 --> 00:08:56,420
I realized it was all too real.

215
00:08:56,750 --> 00:08:58,010
I originally assumed

216
00:08:58,030 --> 00:08:59,770
you just paid lip service to patriotism.

217
00:09:00,120 --> 00:09:02,250
You seemed to be greedy,

218
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:05,100
but you did donate money

219
00:09:05,670 --> 00:09:06,540
and supplies.

220
00:09:11,360 --> 00:09:12,700
Why do I feel like

221
00:09:13,750 --> 00:09:15,340
I'm losing money on this deal?

222
00:09:15,720 --> 00:09:16,580
Mr. Tian,

223
00:09:16,990 --> 00:09:19,180
you didn't give a single coin,

224
00:09:19,270 --> 00:09:21,940
yet you thwarted Xia Yuan's plot

225
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:24,180
and avenged yourself on Chu Shaohua.

226
00:09:24,750 --> 00:09:26,180
Seems you came out ahead.

227
00:09:29,870 --> 00:09:30,540
Agreed.

228
00:09:47,470 --> 00:09:48,130
Signed?

229
00:09:49,230 --> 00:09:50,100
Shipment departs tomorrow.

230
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:56,560
[28 January, 1932]

231
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:22,420
Make way!

232
00:10:22,920 --> 00:10:23,730
Move aside!

233
00:10:24,080 --> 00:10:24,810
Move aside!

234
00:10:25,160 --> 00:10:26,060
Make way!

235
00:10:26,350 --> 00:10:27,140
Make way!

236
00:10:28,160 --> 00:10:28,690
Hurry up!

237
00:10:29,750 --> 00:10:30,450
Careful!

238
00:10:33,230 --> 00:10:34,660
Where cannon fire roared,

239
00:10:36,800 --> 00:10:38,260
homes were razed.

240
00:10:40,470 --> 00:10:42,060
Survivors cried out in mourning.

241
00:10:42,680 --> 00:10:44,060
Bodies piled beyond the passes.

242
00:10:44,350 --> 00:10:45,500
Blood stained the Huangpu River red.

243
00:10:45,800 --> 00:10:47,610
What crime did we commit to suffer this?

244
00:10:49,630 --> 00:10:51,140
It

245
00:10:51,710 --> 00:10:53,970
means never merely our homeland,

246
00:10:55,750 --> 00:10:57,690
but our very dignity

247
00:10:58,870 --> 00:11:00,060
and our deepest convictions

248
00:11:01,200 --> 00:11:02,850
are all trampled ruthlessly

249
00:11:03,560 --> 00:11:05,180
by the invaders.

250
00:11:17,920 --> 00:11:18,450
Bai.

251
00:11:18,950 --> 00:11:19,570
Sun.

252
00:11:21,200 --> 00:11:21,690
Bai.

253
00:11:21,710 --> 00:11:22,420
Sun.

254
00:11:23,280 --> 00:11:24,020
Bai.

255
00:11:24,160 --> 00:11:24,900
Sun.

256
00:11:27,440 --> 00:11:28,330
- Sun.
- Bai.

257
00:11:29,080 --> 00:11:30,090
Are you okay?

258
00:11:30,950 --> 00:11:32,420
I didn't find you
at Spring Garden Restaurant.

259
00:11:32,440 --> 00:11:33,260
I was scared to death!

260
00:11:33,440 --> 00:11:34,570
Was it bombed?

261
00:11:34,680 --> 00:11:35,420
No,

262
00:11:35,440 --> 00:11:36,500
but all the staff fled.

263
00:11:36,750 --> 00:11:38,140
I've got many priceless treasures there!

264
00:11:38,160 --> 00:11:39,060
Bai,

265
00:11:39,590 --> 00:11:40,570
in this case,

266
00:11:40,590 --> 00:11:41,780
just be glad you're safe!

267
00:11:42,590 --> 00:11:43,970
Why are you dressed like this?

268
00:11:45,800 --> 00:11:47,060
I've joined the 19th Route Army,

269
00:11:47,560 --> 00:11:48,900
heading to Wusong with the troops soon.

270
00:11:49,320 --> 00:11:50,420
Came here to say goodbye.

271
00:11:50,520 --> 00:11:51,930
So abruptly?

272
00:11:52,560 --> 00:11:53,780
Don't go. Stay with me!

273
00:11:53,800 --> 00:11:54,930
I'm going to fight the Japanese!

274
00:11:55,830 --> 00:11:57,420
Don't leave. Please stay!

275
00:11:57,440 --> 00:11:58,850
I... I beg you.

276
00:11:59,320 --> 00:12:00,140
I have to go.

277
00:12:00,830 --> 00:12:01,610
No.

278
00:12:02,110 --> 00:12:03,210
Don't go, please.

279
00:12:03,630 --> 00:12:04,260
Don't leave.

280
00:12:04,350 --> 00:12:05,730
Sun, I'm so scared.

281
00:12:09,590 --> 00:12:10,420
Had you asked me before,

282
00:12:11,990 --> 00:12:13,810
I would've stayed without hesitation.

283
00:12:14,280 --> 00:12:15,090
But now the Japanese

284
00:12:15,110 --> 00:12:16,210
have reached our doorstep.

285
00:12:16,230 --> 00:12:17,970
If I don't stand up now,

286
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:20,090
our nation will be annihilated.

287
00:12:20,560 --> 00:12:22,090
I know, but please don't leave!

288
00:12:22,110 --> 00:12:22,900
I have to go.

289
00:12:23,630 --> 00:12:24,210
Trust me.

290
00:12:25,680 --> 00:12:26,660
I'll come back for sure.

291
00:12:27,800 --> 00:12:28,500
- Bai.
- No.

292
00:12:30,200 --> 00:12:30,850
Wait for me.

293
00:12:30,870 --> 00:12:31,500
No!

294
00:12:31,950 --> 00:12:33,180
Don't go, Sun!

295
00:12:42,230 --> 00:12:43,930
All prepared medicines sold out?

296
00:12:44,110 --> 00:12:44,780
Yes.

297
00:12:45,160 --> 00:12:46,300
