298
00:12:46,400 --> 00:12:47,300
Already underway.

299
00:12:47,560 --> 00:12:49,420
New stocks will hit shelves tomorrow.

300
00:12:51,440 --> 00:12:52,060
Hongnian,

301
00:12:52,800 --> 00:12:54,540
