315
00:13:17,750 --> 00:13:19,330
Don't care about our reputation?

316
00:13:19,870 --> 00:13:21,570
Fine. Starting tomorrow,

317
00:13:21,800 --> 00:13:23,930
all prepared medicines doubled in price.

318
00:13:24,560 --> 00:13:27,380
But reserve 10% of trauma-specific drugs

319
00:13:27,590 --> 00:13:28,500
to donate to the front lines.

320
00:13:29,040 --> 00:13:31,020
