[United Against the Enemy]

325
00:13:52,040 --> 00:13:53,380
How far are we
from the command headquarters?

326
00:13:56,080 --> 00:13:58,690
There should be a bridge up ahead.

327
00:13:59,470 --> 00:14:00,540
Cross it, and we'll arrive.

328
00:14:02,470 --> 00:14:04,320
[Rallying for National Crisis]

329
00:14:32,990 --> 00:14:33,780
Greetings.

330
00:14:35,920 --> 00:14:38,210
On behalf of the Shanghai TCM Guild,

331
00:14:38,320 --> 00:14:39,850
we're delivering drugs and bandages

332
00:14:39,870 --> 00:14:41,660
to the command headquarters
at Fanzhuang, Zhenru.

333
00:14:42,230 --> 00:14:43,260
The bridge ahead has been blown up,

334
00:14:43,280 --> 00:14:43,930
impassable now.

335
00:14:44,800 --> 00:14:45,570
Can people cross?

336
00:14:45,590 --> 00:14:46,610
We can carry the drugs over.

337
00:14:46,630 --> 00:14:47,420
No.

338
00:14:48,160 --> 00:14:49,020
Oh! Planes!

339
00:14:49,280 --> 00:14:51,090
Take cover now!

340
00:14:51,470 --> 00:14:51,970
Hurry!

341
00:14:52,200 --> 00:14:53,300
Conceal yourselves.

342
00:14:56,040 --> 00:14:57,690
