343
00:15:40,870 --> 00:15:41,610
You're awake.

344
00:15:42,320 --> 00:15:43,930
Dr. Wang, the patient is conscious!

345
00:15:44,560 --> 00:15:45,090
Okay.

346
00:15:50,950 --> 00:15:52,090
Can you hear me speaking?

347
00:15:53,560 --> 00:15:54,140
Sir,

348
00:15:55,590 --> 00:15:57,420
