349
00:15:58,990 --> 00:16:00,970
You were knocked unconscious by bombs.

350
00:16:01,200 --> 00:16:03,140
Sustained minor physical injuries,

351
00:16:04,280 --> 00:16:05,900
plus a concussion to the head.

352
00:16:06,400 --> 00:16:07,380
Nothing too serious.

353
00:16:07,750 --> 00:16:09,970
You'll recover after resting a few days.

354
00:16:13,110 --> 00:16:13,780
Sir,

355
00:16:15,080 --> 00:16:15,810
where

356
00:16:17,710 --> 00:16:18,570
is Mr. Wen?

357
00:16:19,110 --> 00:16:21,180
You mean your companion?

358
00:16:23,080 --> 00:16:23,930
His injuries

359
00:16:24,110 --> 00:16:25,180
are far more severe than yours.

360
00:16:25,520 --> 00:16:26,180
Drink some water.

361
00:16:27,590 --> 00:16:28,540
Are you alright?

362
00:16:31,230 --> 00:16:32,140
What happened?

363
00:16:34,440 --> 00:16:35,900
They're Accountant Zhou's family.

364
00:16:36,040 --> 00:16:37,660
Their home on Xiangshan Road was razed.

365
00:16:37,680 --> 00:16:39,380
Nowhere to go, so they turned to us.

366
00:16:41,080 --> 00:16:42,330
Take them to the back courtyard!

367
00:16:42,710 --> 00:16:43,810
Get some food for the girl.

368
00:16:43,950 --> 00:16:45,300
Thank you.

369
00:16:47,520 --> 00:16:48,610
Where was it bombed?

370
00:16:48,630 --> 00:16:49,330
Xiangshan Road.

371
00:16:50,830 --> 00:16:51,380
Follow me!

372
00:16:51,380 --> 00:16:52,700
[Jujing Apothecary]

373
00:16:52,710 --> 00:16:53,780
Head to Xiangshan Road!

374
