Erniu!

375
00:17:10,720 --> 00:17:11,410
Erniu!

376
00:17:12,670 --> 00:17:13,610
Erniu!

377
00:17:16,110 --> 00:17:16,890
Erniu!

378
00:17:17,430 --> 00:17:18,130
Erniu!

379
00:17:18,150 --> 00:17:18,740
Don't stop me.

380
00:17:18,760 --> 00:17:19,370
Danger!

381
00:17:20,520 --> 00:17:21,130
Danger!

382
00:17:49,280 --> 00:17:50,370
This is her shoe!

383
00:17:50,830 --> 00:17:51,740
Her shoe!

384
00:17:52,390 --> 00:17:53,980
She didn't leave.

385
00:17:54,080 --> 00:17:55,060
She must be here somewhere!

386
00:17:55,280 --> 00:17:56,260
She has to be around here!

387
00:17:56,520 --> 00:17:58,060
Erniu!

388
00:17:59,830 --> 00:18:00,650
Erniu!

389
00:18:02,590 --> 00:18:03,700
What are you waiting for?

390
00:18:03,720 --> 00:18:04,700
Go get help.

391
00:18:04,720 --> 00:18:05,650
Call an ambulance!

392
00:18:07,040 --> 00:18:07,700
Erniu!

393
00:18:09,080 --> 00:18:09,850
Erniu!

394
00:18:11,280 --> 00:18:13,060
Are you there? Say something!

395
00:18:38,040 --> 00:18:40,090
He sustained head injuries.

396
00:18:40,630 --> 00:18:41,570
Generally speaking,

397
00:18:42,000 --> 00:18:43,300
after brain surgery,

398
00:18:44,040 --> 00:18:45,260
the sooner he regains consciousness,
the better.

399
00:18:46,670 --> 00:18:50,220
If he remains unconscious
beyond seven days,

400
00:18:51,190 --> 00:18:52,260
the situation will become critical.

401
00:19:02,480 --> 00:19:03,500
Am I still alive?

402
00:19:05,630 --> 00:19:06,170
Yes,

403
00:19:07,670 --> 00:19:08,300
you are.

404
00:19:10,190 --> 00:19:10,890
Don't worry.

405
00:19:12,150 --> 00:19:12,850
As long as I'm here,

406
00:19:14,630 --> 00:19:15,740
