[Doctor's Office]
Sir, today is the sixth day,

409
00:19:41,520 --> 00:19:43,980
yet he shows no signs of waking up.

410
00:19:44,560 --> 00:19:45,370
Keep waiting.

411
00:19:47,590 --> 00:19:49,090
No other options left?

412
00:19:49,480 --> 00:19:51,700
We've tried all conceivable treatment

413
00:19:52,350 --> 00:19:54,300
and all possible medications.

414
00:19:55,430 --> 00:19:56,300
Now

415
00:19:57,110 --> 00:19:58,420
it's up to his fate.

416
00:20:27,000 --> 00:20:28,940
The general fell from his horse

417
00:20:29,680 --> 00:20:31,940
and lay unconscious for seven days.

418
00:20:32,720 --> 00:20:34,370
Three imperial physicians came and went,

419
00:20:34,590 --> 00:20:36,140
yet he did not rouse from his coma.

420
00:20:37,000 --> 00:20:38,290
The general's mother thought

421
00:20:38,750 --> 00:20:40,380
that might as well give it a shot,

422
00:20:41,510 --> 00:20:43,460
so she summoned your great-grandfather.

423
00:20:43,480 --> 00:20:44,490
Guess what happened next?

424
00:20:44,510 --> 00:20:45,460
Well?

425
00:20:45,750 --> 00:20:48,770
He gave him two Miracle Pills,

426
00:20:49,240 --> 00:20:50,250
one taken internally

427
00:20:50,550 --> 00:20:51,620
and the other applied externally.

428
00:20:52,030 --> 00:20:53,290
Within less than two hours,

429
00:20:53,830 --> 00:20:57,490
the general
slowly regained consciousness!

430
00:22:07,200 --> 00:22:09,220
This is our Chu family's Miracle Pill

431
00:22:09,240 --> 00:22:10,940
crafted through over 100 steps.

432
00:22:11,320 --> 00:22:12,980
Not one can be omitted.

433
00:22:34,590 --> 00:22:35,730
Here, take a whiff.

434
00:22:36,580 --> 00:22:38,140
This is the scent of Miracle Pill.

435
00:23:50,920 --> 00:23:52,010
Let's talk out there.

436
00:23:59,880 --> 00:24:01,460
Today marks the seventh day.

437
00:24:03,200 --> 00:24:04,730
As his family member,

438
00:24:05,280 --> 00:24:06,250
start preparing yourselves.

439
00:24:09,210 --> 00:24:15,130
♪A blanket lying on the snow♪

440
00:24:15,770 --> 00:24:21,250
♪Melting frost in silent glow♪

441
00:24:22,090 --> 00:24:25,010
♪On endless snowy roads, I roam♪

442
00:24:25,790 --> 00:24:26,940
Study this prescription.

443
00:24:27,550 --> 00:24:28,330
Use it flexibly!

444
00:24:29,440 --> 00:24:30,570
Even for the same symptoms,

445
00:24:31,030 --> 00:24:33,530
adapt to age differences,

446
00:24:34,000 --> 00:24:35,090
gender contrasts,

447
00:24:35,350 --> 00:24:36,730
seasonal variations,

448
00:24:37,160 --> 00:24:38,290
and regional specificities.

449
00:24:38,680 --> 00:24:39,330
Remember?

450
00:24:39,880 --> 00:24:41,010
Yes, Grandpa.

451
00:24:41,930 --> 00:24:47,650
♪Warming slowly every part of his heart♪

452
00:24:47,970 --> 00:24:51,130
♪He whispers spring is near♪

453
00:24:51,130 --> 00:24:54,050
♪He says winter is brief♪

454
00:24:54,610 --> 00:24:57,270
♪The eternal shore♪

455
00:24:57,270 --> 00:25:00,360
♪Calls out once more♪

456
00:25:00,840 --> 00:25:06,930
♪The dark night rages,
fierce and without restraint♪

457
00:25:07,130 --> 00:25:13,720
♪The smoke of battle hangs heavy,
and weary steps falter♪

458
00:25:14,010 --> 00:25:17,280
♪Sunbeams kiss the wheat ears tenderly♪

459
00:25:17,530 --> 00:25:20,770
♪Shining with the poet's
blood and sweat♪

460
00:25:20,930 --> 00:25:25,550
♪The soil before dawn
is always buried in darkness♪

461
00:25:25,590 --> 00:25:28,140
My plan is to use
the Western pharmaceutical principles

462
00:25:28,160 --> 00:25:30,770
to reform and improve
traditional ready-made prescriptions.

463
00:25:31,000 --> 00:25:33,380
I believe by using
the Western pharmaceutical principles

464
00:25:33,400 --> 00:25:34,900
and their manufacturing techniques,

465
00:25:35,270 --> 00:25:38,900
we can undoubtedly elevate TCM.

466
00:25:40,090 --> 00:25:43,410
♪Flames light the way
where despair once lay♪

467
00:25:43,730 --> 00:25:46,870
♪I shield you, my very soul entwined♪

468
00:25:47,370 --> 00:25:52,200
♪Through hardship, to the goal♪

469
00:25:52,200 --> 00:25:55,780
♪We reach, at last♪

470
00:25:55,780 --> 00:25:57,930
♪The shore we hold fast♪

471
00:26:21,500 --> 00:26:27,590
♪The dark night rages,
fierce and without restraint♪

472
00:26:30,360 --> 00:26:31,100
Zhiqiu,

473
00:26:31,100 --> 00:26:34,380
♪The smoke of battle hangs heavy,
and weary steps falter♪

474
00:26:35,580 --> 00:26:36,580
the Miracle Pill

475
00:26:37,800 --> 00:26:39,730
dispels blood stasis and stops bleeding.

476
00:26:39,730 --> 00:26:41,430
♪Shining with the poet's
blood and sweat♪

477
00:26:42,420 --> 00:26:43,420
It invigorates blood flow
to relieve pain,

478
00:26:43,420 --> 00:26:45,680
♪The soil before dawn
is always buried in darkness♪

479
00:26:45,680 --> 00:26:46,860
and neutralizes toxins
to reduce swelling.

480
00:26:47,510 --> 00:26:50,270
♪Fate, day by day, earnest and brave,
leaves no regrets♪

481
00:26:50,270 --> 00:26:52,140
