00:26:56,880 --> 00:26:58,530
Following Grandpa's guidance,

484
00:27:01,400 --> 00:27:04,100
I subtly adjusted the prescription.

485
00:27:04,390 --> 00:27:07,510
♪I shield you, my very soul entwined♪

486
00:27:07,510 --> 00:27:08,940
Just as you suggested,

487
00:27:09,790 --> 00:27:11,050
I embraced diverse approaches

488
00:27:13,550 --> 00:27:15,690
and refined the production process.

489
00:27:15,690 --> 00:27:17,010
♪Through hardship, to the goal♪

490
00:27:17,010 --> 00:27:17,990
♪We reach, at last♪

491
00:27:17,990 --> 00:27:18,590
♪The shore we hold fast♪

492
00:27:30,310 --> 00:27:32,140
Every step was flawless.

493
00:27:34,790 --> 00:27:36,380
Why won't you awaken?

494
00:27:37,640 --> 00:27:39,330
Please wake up,

495
00:27:42,030 --> 00:27:44,460
for the sake of Miracle Pill,

496
00:27:47,350 --> 00:27:48,620
and for the countless trials

497
00:27:49,720 --> 00:27:51,620
