498
00:28:05,270 --> 00:28:06,090
Wen Zhiqiu,

499
00:28:06,920 --> 00:28:07,940
you said

500
00:28:09,350 --> 00:28:10,980
you wanted to make Wen's Pharmacy

501
00:28:11,000 --> 00:28:12,900
Shanghai's top pharmacy.

502
00:28:17,200 --> 00:28:18,530
If you keep lying,

503
00:28:19,440 --> 00:28:20,420
forget about the top pharmacy;

504
00:28:20,790 --> 00:28:22,570
