507
00:28:33,240 --> 00:28:35,220
Stand up if you can't stomach defeat.

508
00:28:44,160 --> 00:28:46,570
We've weathered every storm.

509
00:28:51,750 --> 00:28:53,420
A true man settles scores when wronged!

510
00:28:54,480 --> 00:28:56,810
We must seek revenge on the Japanese.

511
00:28:57,640 --> 00:28:59,290
You won't collapse now!

512
00:28:59,830 --> 00:29:00,770
Stand up!

513
00:29:01,440 --> 00:29:03,420
We'll seek revenge.

514
00:29:13,880 --> 00:29:17,220
You mean "Mountains bear trees
