527
00:29:56,620 --> 00:29:59,560
♪Let my breath run ragged, run ragged♪

528
00:30:00,070 --> 00:30:02,450
do I realize I can't live without you.

529
00:30:02,450 --> 00:30:04,360
♪Lost in love,
how could I ever fool myself again?♪

530
00:30:04,360 --> 00:30:06,530
