532
00:30:08,970 --> 00:30:11,840
♪When you and I bloom
into an entwined mystery♪

533
00:30:12,480 --> 00:30:17,800
♪As we walk toward the same thorns♪

534
00:30:17,880 --> 00:30:19,900
