535
00:30:19,900 --> 00:30:23,920
♪Like a fish stranded on land,
you stay silent♪

536
00:30:23,920 --> 00:30:25,450
I cannot afford to lose you.

537
00:30:25,450 --> 00:30:30,120
♪For you, I dive deep beneath the sea♪

538
00:30:30,670 --> 00:30:35,160
♪If I had once surrendered to destiny♪

539
00:30:35,160 --> 00:30:35,820
Zhiqiu,

540
00:30:36,790 --> 00:30:37,690
I promise you this.

541
00:30:37,990 --> 00:30:39,180
If only you wake up,

542
00:30:39,180 --> 00:30:40,920
♪Then meeting you
was always meant to be♪

543
00:30:40,920 --> 00:30:42,010
I will marry you.

544
00:30:43,360 --> 00:30:48,520
♪Turn around and forget myself♪

545
00:30:49,240 --> 00:30:54,520
♪You guard my most cherished heart♪

546
00:30:55,200 --> 00:31:00,920
♪Let me decide how I return♪

547
00:31:01,320 --> 00:31:06,770
♪Even if storms urge us to flee♪

548
00:31:07,600 --> 00:31:12,840
♪How could I ever leave you?♪

549
00:31:13,640 --> 00:31:18,920
♪A lifelong riddle without an answer♪

550
00:31:19,960 --> 00:31:25,160
♪This very day,
I see through fate's scheming♪

551
00:31:25,960 --> 00:31:32,760
♪To make our destiny mine,
with you written in♪

552
00:31:42,800 --> 00:31:47,560
[Public Shanghai Hospital]

553
00:31:49,390 --> 00:31:50,570
Let me take a break.

554
00:31:50,920 --> 00:31:52,940
