590
00:33:57,070 --> 00:33:58,050
I think

591
00:33:58,680 --> 00:34:00,050
if Xia Chu knew

592
00:34:00,680 --> 00:34:01,700
Shaohua begins anew,

593
00:34:01,960 --> 00:34:03,290
