594
00:34:06,280 --> 00:34:07,980
Now, I alone

595
00:34:09,190 --> 00:34:10,130
still remember him.

596
00:34:11,630 --> 00:34:12,980
How quickly time flies!

597
00:34:13,630 --> 00:34:14,530
In the blink of an eye,

598
00:34:14,960 --> 00:34:16,050
