603
00:34:36,070 --> 00:34:37,210
Does the Miracle Pill

604
00:34:39,000 --> 00:34:39,980
really work that well?

605
00:34:40,520 --> 00:34:41,300
Absolutely!

606
00:34:42,360 --> 00:34:45,420
Just her father and Shaozhong

607
00:34:45,440 --> 00:34:46,980
