648
00:36:42,520 --> 00:36:44,130
Great! You're the owner now.

649
00:36:44,150 --> 00:36:44,900
Congratulations!

650
00:36:44,920 --> 00:36:46,250
Thanks. Just a small business.

651
00:36:48,060 --> 00:36:49,860
I later heard what happened

652
00:36:50,040 --> 00:36:51,020
between you and Mr. Xia.

653
00:36:54,360 --> 00:36:54,980
Your husband?

654
00:36:55,920 --> 00:36:56,460
Yes.

655
00:36:58,000 --> 00:36:59,530
Seeing you live a new life now

656
00:37:00,040 --> 00:37:00,940
makes me happy.

657
00:37:01,840 --> 00:37:02,460
Thank you.

658
00:37:03,920 --> 00:37:05,980
I think we do have quite a connection.

659
00:37:06,360 --> 00:37:08,090
I think I've met your husband before.

660
00:37:08,520 --> 00:37:09,170
Really?

661
00:37:10,590 --> 00:37:13,460
He called Mr. Xia away that day.

662
00:37:13,710 --> 00:37:15,170
Mr. Xia, here's your bill.

663
00:37:15,360 --> 00:37:16,090
Please check it over.

664
00:37:16,110 --> 00:37:16,650
Alright.

665
00:37:20,800 --> 00:37:21,500
Good day, sir.

666
00:37:21,710 --> 00:37:22,780
May I help you?

667
00:37:22,800 --> 00:37:23,460
My friend.

668
00:37:24,040 --> 00:37:25,690
Very well. I'll serve tea.

669
00:37:25,840 --> 00:37:26,460
Thank you.

670
00:37:50,040 --> 00:37:50,650
Who

671
00:37:52,440 --> 00:37:53,420
